high_descs: Turn and stand in front of the waste basket to the right of the fridge.
Take an apple from the waste basket.
Turn and go right to stand in front of the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave, turn it on, take the apple out and shut the door.
Turn and move to the left and stand at the left edge of the counter.
Put the apple in the waste basket to the left of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple in the waste basket.

high_descs: Turn to the left then walk over to a silver bin.
Pick up the yellow apple from the bin.
Turn around and go to the right to the microwave.
Place the apple inside the microwave. Warm up the apple then take it out of the microwave.
Turn around and go to the left.
Place the apple in the silver bin.
anns.task_desc: Warm up the apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the waste basket to the right of the fridge.
Take the apple from in the waste basket.
Turn around, move forward, turn left, move forward, then turn left to face the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave.
Turn around, move forward, then turn right, to face the counter.
Put the apple in the waste basket, to the left of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple in the trash.
